{"tid":1909681,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam遊戲企劃] 如果我哋都可以成為李超人？","createTime":"2020-03-04T06:44:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T19:27:31.000Z","uid":268272,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ceacb7f203ce87d6005bbe132a58cf008596bd79","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T06:44:50.000Z","msg":"係咁嘅，我哋係炎魔工作室，係一間新開嘅小型本土遊戲studio。<br />\n其實咁多位近排聽過誠哥個名，有冇諗過佢係點樣成為超人呢？我哋其實想重現地產商嘅發跡史，所以就想整個Game去比大家體驗下佢哋嘅發跡史，甚至整返自己嘅地產發跡史。<br />\n<br />\n你哋會問：其實你哋個Game同SimCity有咩分別呢？<br />\n咁SimCity係冇地皮呢個限制，亦都唔會同正苦嘈交，而我哋隻game希望重現返香港起樓嘅過程，同埋金融戇鳩野。仲有simcity要裝摸落去先有新嘅building，而我哋會預先裝定其他style嘅建築物，任君選擇，但係大家亦可以裝mod落去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rx9n1OF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRx9n1OF.jpg&h=91e64b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上圖為不同style的建築物，80年代至千禧年代風格亦有。<br />\n而呢個game會有三個mode：<br />\n創業、上帝同埋故事。<br />\n創業就係當然係好似李超人咁樣創業做首富，而上帝即係sandbox。<br />\n最後就係故事mode。故事mode就係將本身創業mode嘅玩法，再加強難度之餘，再將成個game變成一個視&middot;覺&middot;小&middot;說。<br />\n你冇睇錯我亦都冇打錯，我哋想個故事mode變成一個鬥志之前有令人感動嘅Visual Novel，而文手更加痴線到想請聲優配音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，可惜製作成本同埋請聲優全部都係要錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以我哋要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">集氣！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">突破！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">掙扎！</span><br />\n<br />\n而呢個就係kickstarter 嘅link，希望大家可以入錢支持我哋團隊。多謝咁多位連登巴打睇完呢篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/studio-molo/soaring-tales-of-skylines\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kickstarter.com%2Fprojects%2Fstudio-molo%2Fsoaring-tales-of-skylines&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=6c2783a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/studio-molo/soaring-tales-of-skylines</a>"},{"pid":"173dd653cac3d8018053bc21892c5c7c0bb6c0d6","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"37a6757c00656a4b7dd2f0e05cc2fdfc985f98ba","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T08:53:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9f5baee9554cff22dedff6f677a3b8f9db12058d","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"357f19f73c5c0c7a07210180caf7f27306201c64","tid":1909681,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ecd8dc0ae25b4168ded853b85c1293e929235a","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357f19f73c5c0c7a07210180caf7f27306201c64","tid":1909681,"uid":36911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:47:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"Thx Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88f049fee1357abe6065ca7a8f6caba3df852ff","tid":1909681,"uid":288731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"入去睇咗，個名好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇諗住做2d 先"},{"pid":"8162868400f3405b54c5b8e7f26db36f058c3776","tid":1909681,"uid":258374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:54:04.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"5966d08f2e2e5d551f3a806ede4099c0340f9c4a","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a88f049fee1357abe6065ca7a8f6caba3df852ff","tid":1909681,"uid":288731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"入去睇咗，個名好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇諗住做2d 先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"我地會有2D，但主要都係集中係劇情嗰度<br />\n至於個名果方面<br />\n我覺得放落連登討論先做到集思廣益嘅意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ea93aabe3120ea183fd97ef765df5b3760f828","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T11:21:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"9152e0b79da2412c023960aba014093528b9d512","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T13:46:29.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"013e4b9044498a8d8f13cbacca0f4a93195227b3","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T03:03:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4910c139c35cc123b6ee90e3f07f58f50c251f6a","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b5087a221b5632a075c220a91ab3624b151ccb74","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T13:27:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"179d2656e36db70775142772317c8d68a5b0afaf","tid":1909681,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5966d08f2e2e5d551f3a806ede4099c0340f9c4a","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a88f049fee1357abe6065ca7a8f6caba3df852ff","tid":1909681,"uid":288731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:53:08.000Z","msg":"入去睇咗，個名好柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇諗住做2d 先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"我地會有2D，但主要都係集中係劇情嗰度<br />\n至於個名果方面<br />\n我覺得放落連登討論先做到集思廣益嘅意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T17:25:12.000Z","msg":"唔係好見到個背景細節，或者淨係呢個poet標題啦，好似冇提華進英退、之後世界經濟同英商撤資"},{"pid":"f236781632a716d9bded72e3cf14c5e101302708","tid":1909681,"uid":76570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:16:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ce7fd4a7f2b1ed837971e89c0bb8281433577168","tid":1909681,"uid":21646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T07:58:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油呀 有無其他game比我課住金玩"},{"pid":"fc09c6d868e9066c51a12fb901601cc4914cceea","tid":1909681,"uid":21646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:00:47.000Z","msg":"反而你想做李超人 係咪經營管理玩法會好d"},{"pid":"e063b2d121a5915a846af95deaeb9b736773d8af","tid":1909681,"uid":21646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:03:52.000Z","msg":"傾吓偈姐 我get錯唔好屌"},{"pid":"5464657488c43efdb83e3111b4a898550b52f17b","tid":1909681,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T08:04:23.000Z","msg":"98%魔力寶貝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cac6b02a17f8a8125b20ecdcce02bb7a93c327","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T03:05:12.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8685c220523dd469accac6b314fabc9df735820c","tid":1909681,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"有諗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304e7a7095aa04be6ec6ccedfeb1aef91ffe8de4","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8685c220523dd469accac6b314fabc9df735820c","tid":1909681,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T04:56:17.000Z","msg":"有諗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T05:03:20.000Z","msg":"心動不如行動入錢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ed143a226cb4cc3c1e666c49adc05664684458","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T02:49:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7a8a889244e1aa6eb9f78ac94b9dc7cf476372dd","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T08:25:01.000Z","msg":"陣間會將裏面個英文版翻譯做中文放上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"206614dd146691a7e97fc3c88f47409101675532","tid":1909681,"uid":268272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T10:01:23.000Z","msg":"大家好我是JC<br />\n我們是來自香港的炎魔工作室，我們現在開發以香港房地產來作背景的一個模擬遊戲。<br />\n簡介<br />\n香港經歷過六七十年代的暴動後，經濟開始復甦。而你就是一名想獲得成就的企業家，其他人都跟隨著你的腳步。<br />\n這不是一個簡單的遊戲，這是一個由你寫出來的夢幻故事！<br />\n從簡陋的工廠大廈到西貢的高級洋房，這完全取決於您。從土地招標到建築再到出售公寓建築，您都是決定一切的人！<br />\n你可以成為香港的強人，或者成為一名破產的窮光蛋！<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202003/b63faa42a1fc81deaf76b6e471fa4545.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202003%2Fb63faa42a1fc81deaf76b6e471fa4545.JPG&h=50f3ee70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遊戲開發<br />\n這款遊戲是一種房地產建設的模擬遊戲，而這種遊戲將會以香港甚至全世界的建築風格來作重點。<br />\n50種以上的建築及車輛<br />\n我們製作團隊建設了很多不同的3D立體模型，例如不同年代風格的建築物，當中包括公寓大樓丶商場和辦公室。<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202003/2fdc0c17b2624a9b06709e677e0ac629.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202003%2F2fdc0c17b2624a9b06709e677e0ac629.JPG&h=3db43595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n自由地選擇你的合作夥伴<br />\n合作夥伴包括設計工作室，承包商，發起人和電梯供應商，當中價錢亦會有波動。而且有句古話&ldquo;一分錢一分貨&rdquo;，當您試圖削減成本時，您可能會遭受很多問題！<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202003/d81942e06f6fdb304de65ef766e341ae.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202003%2Fd81942e06f6fdb304de65ef766e341ae.JPG&h=83525ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遊戲之中的建設過程！<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202003/6eff1e73b2ee97d8e7fb4b6f5719fabb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202003%2F6eff1e73b2ee97d8e7fb4b6f5719fabb.JPG&h=936e4cc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不同的工作室有不同的價錢！<br />\n具有全球靈感的特殊設計<br />\n香港是世界著名的國際中心之一，所以建築漂亮，有些超前，而且從未顯得過時。我們的建築物將參考從香港到倫敦和紐約等輝煌建築物，以使我們的建築物從無到有被劃破。<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202003/c1293b3d4070df3de04057fc51d5bbdb.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202003%2Fc1293b3d4070df3de04057fc51d5bbdb.JPG&h=7d6da209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n具現代風格的公寓大廈！<br />\n籌款目標<br />\n如果達成籌款目標，我們會開始故事模式的研發設計多人模式及聘請聲優。這三項計畫將不日解釋。<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n最後如果對我們這個遊戲有興趣，可以點擊我們的kickstarter專頁留意更新動態，甚至資助我們遊戲的開發，多謝大家。<br />\n<a href=\"https://soaring-tales-of-skylines.kckb.st/c95976cf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoaring-tales-of-skylines.kckb.st%2Fc95976cf&d=VxC68O7S0S1nNKmf4pYeIX8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=7afb65e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://soaring-tales-of-skylines.kckb.st/c95976cf</a>"}}